WEBVTT

00:02:29.080 --> 00:02:31.558
shared about eight percent of national [income],

00:02:31.558 --> 00:02:34.232
while the bottom 50 percent of Americans

00:02:34.232 --> 00:02:36.775
shared 18 percent.

00:02:36.775 --> 00:02:40.127
Thirty years later, today, the top one percent

00:02:40.127 --> 00:02:43.749
shares over 20 percent of national [income],

00:02:43.749 --> 00:02:45.650
while the bottom 50 percent of Americans

00:02:45.650 --> 00:02:48.564
share 12 or 13.

00:02:48.564 --> 00:02:51.010
If the trend continues,

00:02:51.010 --> 00:02:52.490
the top one percent will share

00:02:52.490 --> 00:02:54.796
over 30 percent of national [income]

00:02:54.796 --> 00:02:56.588
in another 30 years,

00:02:56.588 --> 00:02:58.868
while the bottom 50 percent of Americans

00:02:58.868 --> 00:03:00.607
will share just six.